data.description: The lovely rc glenwood plan from is full of curb appeal with its welcoming front porch and front yard landscaping. This home features an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an expansive family room. Also enjoy an open dining area, and a charming kitchen fully equipped with energy-efficient appliances, generous counter space, and a roomy pantry for snacking and preparing delicious family meals. Plus, a wonderful back porch to entertain and unwind. Learn more about this home today!
